%U A094547 189046794180,756187176720,3024747985488,12098991941952,48395964882948
%N A094547 a(n) = A019309(n)/4 for n >= 1.
%H A094547 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A094547/b094547.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000</a>
%F A094547 a(2*n+1) = 4*a(2*n); a(2*n) = 4*a(2*n-1)-a(n). - _David Wasserman_, May 22 2007
%F A094547 From _Seiichi Manyama_, Jul 18 2026: (Start)
%F A094547 G.f. A(x) satisfies (1-4*x)*A(x) + A(x^2) = x.
%F A094547 G.f.: Sum_{j>=0} (-1)^j*x^(2^j) / Product_{k=0..j} (1 - 4*x^(2^k)).
%F A094547 a(n) = 4^(n-1) - Sum_{k=1..floor(n/2)} 4^(n-2*k) * a(k). (End)
%Y A094547 Cf. A019309, A045690, A045694.
